full_description:

Speaker: Oliver Bestwalter

Track:PyConDE
This talk is not about how to use pytest. pytest is a good project to explore metaprogramming techniques like introspection and code as data in the context of solving real world problems. 

In this case: implementing a test framework.

Recorded at the PyConDE & PyData Berlin 2019 conference.
https://pycon.de

More details at the conference page: https://de.pycon.org/program/XTD7TE
Twitter:  https://twitter.com/pydataberlin
Twitter:  https://twitter.com/pyconde
